00:49:29.800 --> 00:49:31.590
Which you do.

00:49:31.590 --> 00:49:33.270
RYAN GERMICK: Too beautiful
to be captured on

00:49:33.270 --> 00:49:34.780
film by some cameras.

00:49:34.780 --> 00:49:36.030
JULIE: Exactly.

00:49:38.250 --> 00:49:38.960
Thank you.

00:49:38.960 --> 00:49:40.390
WAYNE WHITE: Thank
you very much.

00:49:40.390 --> 00:49:44.540
I don't why Elaine couldn't
tell me that in person.

00:49:44.540 --> 00:49:47.220
JULIE: We were on the phone on
Friday and she was going to--

00:49:47.220 --> 00:49:49.460
I was trying to talk her
